headline: Consumers Energy Delivers Over $1 Million in Rebates, Cost Savings for Grand Rapids Public Schools
summary: Consumers Energy is proud to partner with Grand Rapids Public Schools to empower one of the state's largest school districts to save money through Consumers Energy's energy efficiency programs.
